  "title": "Class 3 Delivery Driver (Fruits Wholesaler) #81368",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Fruits Wholesaler</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Class 3 Driver</strong></li><li>Working Location: Bedok</li><li>Working Hours: 6 Days, Mon - Fri (6.30am – 6.30pm), Sat (7am – 4pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Incentives + OT + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: 1-Year contract (Renewable/ Convertible to Permanent)</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Drive company vehicle to transport goods safely to assigned locations.</li><li>Load and unload fruits with the help of trolleys and other handling tools.</li><li>Assist in basic warehouse tasks such as arranging, sorting and moving fruit products when required.</li><li>Ensure cleanliness and basic upkeep of the vehicle.</li><li>Follow delivery schedules, work instructions and safety guidelines to support smooth daily operations.</li><li>Perform other ad‑hoc duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Possess valid Class 3 driving license.</li><li>At least 1 year of driving experience in Singapore</li><li>Able to carry load up to 10kg if required.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#81368 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
